ActFisheries Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Northwest Territories Fishery Regulations
PrecisRegulations Amending the NORTHWEST TERRITORIES FISHERY REGULATIONS in order to create one-day sport fishing licences for non-residents and Canadian residents in the Northwest Territories and promote tourism and support businesses offering services to sport fishing enthusiasts from outside the Northwest Territories.
